p.k: Trouble brews in Pontyberry when Michael is fired from the cafe, so he heads down to the bikers' pub to drown his sorrows and bumps into his flirty client Beyonce - leading him to make a monumental mistake that he'll struggle to recover from. UK (2015). Cast: Ruth Jones, Patrick Baladi, Remy Beasley, Ramon Tikaram, Justin Davies, Steve Speirs, Anthony O'Donnell. Director: Simon Massey.
